Class ApplicantRepository

java.lang.Object
Abstract.Repository<Applicant>
Applicant.ApplicantRepository
public class ApplicantRepository extends Repository<Applicant>
Concrete implementation of Repository for managing Applicant entities. Handles loading from and saving to CSV files, and parses Applicant data accordingly.
